of 27 airports and the percentage of on-time arrivals during July,
according to information provided by the airlines to the
Transportation Department and released Thursday.
   The average on-time arrival percentage was 80.5.
   (Departure: The percentage in parentheses reflects the departure
record at the airport.)
   The ranking covers the 27 busiest airports in passenger volume
as determined by the Transportation Department.
