Cineplex Odeon Films Inc. and the King's Court Theater, where the
film is being shown in Pittsburgh.
   Plaintiffs Michael Greb, Paul Metzger and Betti Logan, in
demanding the new title, say that for Universal to call the film
fiction is a lie used to ``blaspheme Christ with unlicensed
freedom.''
