<HEAD>Unwed Malaysian Couple Fined After Living Together For 24 Years</HEAD>
<DATELINE>KUALA LUMPUR, Malaysia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A Moslem religious court on
Thursday fined an unwed couple $570 for committing illicit sex
after the two lived together for 24 years and produced seven
